The paper deals with image feature extraction and face recognition, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of probabilistic framework and EM algorithm also suggests the involvement of information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
